metadata.name: THAT WHICH HOLDS ME BACK
metadata.description:
SOMETHING KEEPS HOLDING ME BACK  
I CAN'T TELL WHAT IT IS

NUMBING MY WILL TO ATTACK  
NOW A RECURRING THEME

MY SWORD BREATHES FIRE IN MY HAND  
ACHING FOR BLOOD TO SPILL

THOUGHTS BRING TEARS RIGHT TO MY EYES  
EMOTIONS I SHAN'T REVEAL

ITS ALL GONE IN AN INSTANT  
THE HOPE FOR PEACE

I AM BACK TO MY RIGHT MIND  
AND HERE TO BEGIN
